FBIS4-16021 "drsov071_d_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-071 Daily Report 13 Apr 1994 Regional Affairs Balakovo AES Power Unit Shut Down Balakovo AES Power Unit Shut Down PM1304103394 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA in Russian 13 Apr 94 First Edition p 8 PM1304103394 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA Russian BFN [Unattributed report: "Balakovo AES Turbine Shut Down"] [Text] An insulator failure tripped the generator safety mechanism at the Balakovo AES [nuclear power station] No. 3 power unit. The turbine has been shut down. Once the trouble had been eliminated, the unit was set on 80-percent capacity. There has been no change in the radiation situation.
